'''Cularin Central Broadcasting''' was a media corporation located on [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]], providing news and entertainment to its viewers. Many inhabitants of Cularin felt that the company was biased toward the [[Thaereian military]]. One of their reporters was [[Yara Grugara]]. Other employees included [[Raouul]], [[Ryk Osentay]] and [[Melanda Forswoth]].

